msgstr "Security Hardening Plan"

#: ../../tutorial/security_plan_cn.md:3
msgid "说明"
msgstr "Description"

#: ../../tutorial/security_plan_cn.md:5
msgid ""
"在面对不可知任务场景或未知代码执行的场景中，建议使用进程安全沙箱 "
"[NsJail](https://github.com/google/nsjail) 保障运行时安全以及使用安全容器 "
"[Kata](https://github.com/kata-containers/kata-containers)  保障容器安全。"
msgstr ""
"In scenarios with unknown tasks or unknown code execution, it is recommended to use the process security sandbox [NsJail](https://github.com/google/nsjail) to ensure runtime security and the secure container [Kata](https://github.com/kata-containers/kata-containers) to ensure container security."

#: ../../tutorial/security_plan_cn.md:7
msgid "SecretFlow 支持通过 NsJail 启动，这使得 SecretFlow 任务可以在安全沙箱中运行，增强任务运行时的安全性。"
msgstr "SecretFlow supports starting with NsJail, which allows SecretFlow tasks to run in a secure sandbox, enhancing the security of task execution."

#: ../../tutorial/security_plan_cn.md:9
msgid "在安全沙箱中运行 SecretFlow 任务"
msgstr "Running SecretFlow Tasks in a Secure Sandbox"

#: ../../tutorial/security_plan_cn.md:11
msgid ""
"基于 Kuscia 框架， 您可以快速体验在安全沙箱中运行 SecretFlow "
"任务，这里以部署中心化组网模式为例，关于更多的部署细节请参考[快速入门](../getting_started/quickstart_cn.md)。"
msgstr ""
"Based on the Kuscia framework, you can quickly experience running SecretFlow tasks in a secure sandbox. Here, we use the deployment of centralized networking mode as an example. For more deployment details, please refer to [Quick Start](../getting_started/quickstart_cn.md)."

